author: Daniel Leighton
title: Daniel Leighton
text: I've been on e-cigs for nine years, since they day they started selling disposables in gas stations for $25 a pop. They'd last four hours at best. It took awhile, going back and forth between real cigs and e-cigs, but I eventually came across totallywicked. No ifs, ands or buts, they are THE best.
